nt-family: 宋体; line-height: 40px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 21px;\">入学要求</span></span></strong><strong style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 40px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 21px;\">/</span></span></strong><strong style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 40px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 21px;\">适合对象：</span></span></strong></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 40px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">(1).</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">专科及其以上学历，电气工程及其自动化、自动化、智能建筑或者电气相关专业在校生（大二及以上学生），刚开始从事电气设计或者准备从事电气设计人员。<br/></span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">(2).</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">专科以下学历、有1年以上相关工作经验，非本专业者或相似专业人员。<br/></span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">(3).</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">先修课程：电工学等基础课。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 40px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 21px;\">2.</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 21px;\">培训内容及预期效果:</span></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">2.1.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">电气施工图设计范围：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(1).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">商业及商业办公楼（强、弱电系统设计）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(2).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">多层住宅（强、弱电系统设计）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(3).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">小高层住宅楼（二类高层）（强、弱电系统及消防系统设计）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(4).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">综合楼、办公楼或学校建筑（强、弱电系统及消防系统设计）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">2.2.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">电气设计内容包括：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(1).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">系统设计。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(2).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">电气施工图设计。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(3).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">电气设计计算（负荷计算、照度计算、雷击次数、导线载流量计算）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(4).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">设备选型（断路器、配电箱选型、导线选型、导线穿管直径选型、桥架与线槽计算）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 14px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(5).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">重要规范精讲分析（结合图纸案例讲解、分析常用的最新规范、图集等）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">2.3.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">“电气设计”三大方面：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 34px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">2.3.1.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">强电设计:</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 255); font-family: 宋体;\">①.供配电系统设计（建筑各类用电负荷等级确定、三相单、相配电确定等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 255); font-family: 宋体;\">②.照明系统设计（根据照明设计标准确认建筑照度标准、灯具选型等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 255); font-family: 宋体;\">③.断路器选型设计(根据接地形式、是否需要设置漏电保护等进行断路器选型、设计)；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 255); font-family: 宋体;\">④.电缆、导线选型（根据计算电流选择断路器、根据载流量选择电缆型号等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 255); font-family: 宋体;\">⑤.线路敷设（根据规范要求进行线路敷设设计等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 255); font-family: 宋体;\">⑥.插座设计（根据不同类型的建筑功能进行插座选型、布置等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 255); font-family: 宋体;\">⑦</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 255); font-family: 宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 255); font-family: 宋体;\">防雷接地设计（根据防雷规范等确认建筑防雷等级、接地形式，按照防雷措施进行防雷设计）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 34px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">2.3.2.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">弱电设计:</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 19px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">①.有线电视系统（有线电视系统一般规定、设计原则、系统构成等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 19px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">②.通信系统（通信系统一般要求、进线、弱电箱布置、电话插孔数量位置确定等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 19px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">③.计算机网络系统（计算机网络系统规定、要求、设置等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 19px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">④.广播系统（住宅根据需要设置广播系统、公共建筑应设置广播系统等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 19px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">⑤.综合布线系统（含通信网络、计算机网络）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 19px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">⑥</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">可视对讲系统（住宅应设置可视对讲访客系统等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.3.3.</span></strong>&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">火灾自动报警与联动控制系统设计：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">①</span></strong><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">火灾自动报警系统分类（根据火灾自动报警设计规范进行分类）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 42px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">②</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">火灾自动报警系统是否需要做（根据建筑设计防火规范确认本建筑是否需要做，属于哪一类）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 42px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">③</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">火灾自动报警系统如何做（根据火灾自动报警规范确认如何做）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 42px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">④</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">火灾自动报警系统设备选型（根据规范选择报警系统的设备型号等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 42px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">⑤</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">.</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">火灾自动报警与联动控制系统（根据规范确认建筑做哪一类报警系统、联动控制系统）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 42px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">（根据规范确认建筑是否需要做火灾自动报警系统、联动控制系统，以及确定如何去做等）；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 40px; text-indent: 28px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">2.4.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">精讲规范：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(1).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">《民用建筑电气设计规范》JGJ16-2008</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(2).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">《供配电系统设计规范》GB50052-2009</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(3).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">《住宅建筑电气设计规范》JGJ242-2011</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(4).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">《建筑照明设计标准》GB50034-2013</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(5).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">《低压配电设计规范》GB50054-2011</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(6).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">《建筑物防雷设计规范》GB 50057-2010</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(7).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">《火灾自动报警系统设计规范》GB50116-2013</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(8).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">《建筑设计防火规范》GB50016-2014</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(9).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">《建筑电气常用数据》04DX101-1</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 28px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">2.5.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">案例分析：实际项目精讲</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(1).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">（多层商铺）电气施工图。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(2).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">（多层购物中心商业）电气施工图。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 35px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">（3）.(6层住宅楼)电气施工图。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(4). (11</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">层住宅)电气施工图。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(5). (18</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">层住宅)电气施工图</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(6).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">（多层办公楼）电气施工图</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 42px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(7). (</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">多层社区综合楼）电气施工图</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 42px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">备注：（所有图纸均为合肥某甲级设计院已经出图的施工图纸，有些项目正在施工中…）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 28px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">2.6.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-family: 黑体;\">预期培训效果：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 58px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">(1).</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">培训合格学员能够进入设计院从事多层住宅、小高层住宅、商业建筑、办公楼以电气施工图设计。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 58px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">(2).</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">能够从事“助理电气设计师”工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 58px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">备注：一般毕业生进入设计院实习需要10个月左右才能上手跟着师傅画图，本次培训可以缩短毕业生实习时间，培训结束后进入设计院2-3个月即可参与设计院图纸的修改、套图、图纸设计等工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 21px;\">3.</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 21px;\">授课讲师：</span></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 49px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">、讲师一：余老师，高级工程师，合肥市某甲级设计院高工，从事电气设计十年，实战能力强，并一直亲自从事各种大中小型工程项目施工图设计、审图工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 49px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">、讲师二栾老师，国家注册电气工程师（供配电），设计院六年从事设计工作，实战能力强，并一直亲自从事各种工程项目施工图设计。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 49px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">、讲师三、根据招生情况再确定安排某甲级院有资深设计经验的工程师。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">备注：实战能力培训为主，理论教学为辅，只为实际应用，不做应试教学。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 21px;\">4.</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 21px;\">学习教材：</span></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">培训班提供：全部电子版资料+部分印刷版设计要点及总结</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(1).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">电气设计软件+软件使用教程。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 28px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">(2).</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体;\">培训用图纸（商业+住宅+办公楼